reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Power and Style Unite: Gaming Desk is a Winning Combination!
reviews.reviewText: I recently upgraded my gaming setup with the Pink Gaming Desk equipped with Power Outlets, and it has completely transformed my gaming experience. This desk is not just a piece of furniture; it's a statement of style and functionality that caters to both aesthetics and the practical needs of a gamer.The inclusion of power outlets is a game-changer. The convenience of having built-in electrical outlets right on the desk eliminates the need for messy extension cords and ensures that all my gaming peripherals and devices are easily powered up. It's a thoughtful feature that speaks to the practical needs of a modern gamer.Assembly was surprisingly straightforward, thanks to clear instructions and well-labeled parts. The sturdiness of the desk once assembled instills confidence that it will withstand the rigors of daily use.If you're looking to upgrade your gaming space with a desk that stands out, provides ample power, and keeps everything organized, I highly recommend this pink gaming desk. It's a delightful addition to any gaming enthusiast's room!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We love these desks. Replaced two ugly old mismatched ones. These are simple but cute, and work really well. Two laptops or two monitors fit. Not much storage at all, keep that in mind. And the workspace is narrow - I got a desk extender that works perfectly for my arms.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My son picked it out, it arrived well packaged. No issues putting it together. It’s not the sturdiest desk he’s ever had but I don’t see it falling apart on him, it’ll suffice. If he was young and rough, I’d be worried but he’s 17, and using it for his xbox. It’s a cool desk and the lights are a nice bonus and one of the reasons he picked it. No complaints.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars nice desk, great customer support
reviews.reviewText: Got two of these, and they went together easily enough, black carbon fiber, looks just like the picture, sturdy, looks nice, led's work. Great price Unfortunately - one of the two desks was little bit damaged on a corner of the table top when it came - though that side could be turned to the wall and almost completely hidden. The other desk was perfect. I sent an email given in the instructions to Bestier customer support. They responded within a half day. After requesting photos, they offerred various solutions, kept communicating regularly, and long story short, they backed up their product and took care of it. Happy owner of two great desks for not a lot of money. If not for the very slight damage on one of them, totally 5 stars

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better than I thought!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this desk to have something in my guest bedroom. I am a new homeowner in school, so I needed something affordable but still aesthetically pleasing. This product's color and style matched what I was going for in the spare bedroom. I took a chance because it wasn't super expensive. It took me less than an hour to build, instructions are easy to follow for assembly and the desk has a lot more leg space than I expected compared to another desk I purchased from Amazon for my home office. This desk is high enough for you to have any small office chairs to their highest setting and still have more than enough space. (perfect for shorter and taller persons) I only rated the sturdiness as 4 stars only because this is a lighter weight product so is much easier to move on your own but, other than that, I'm going to keep it! I'd definitely buy again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So far so good!
reviews.reviewText: We bought this for my daughter for Christmas so that she can have her first gaming set up in her room, plenty of room for all of her equipment, loving the LED lights, and so far the quality seems great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I purchased this desk for my 8 year old daughter. The desk was super easy to assemble, and instructions were very clear. I assembled it by myself with 30min. Despite some markings in the pattern that somewhat resemble scratch marks, the gray looks sleek and modern. The shelves are adjustable and are perfect for organization and saving space on the desk. The led light strip is such a cool touch. It offers a variety of colors and modes for alternating and blinking color lights. My daughter loves the desk. I highly recommended and would definitely purchase this desk in the future should the need arise again.

reviews.reviewerName: Very pretty colors my favorite is the glitter it looks amazing! Awesome quality! I’d bought more colors as well!
reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome great size!
reviews.reviewText: My son loved it easy set up and quick too very simple instructions over all it was and is awesome! Could have more led lights for the price and title of the product. It only comes with one small strip. HUGE ISSUE AND ONLY DOWN FALL FOR US WITH ALLLLLL THE FIBER GLASS ON THIS DESK! It was all over the place! Not cool I have it all over me and it itches!

Desk is well made and easy to assemble, and is great for small gaming and work set-ups. The RGB lights that go under the top shelf are a nice added touch for some mood lighting, as well as the pouch that hangs off of the side.My only issue is that the shelf made to hold the tower is not big enough for my gaming rig, and as a result, I had to get a cart in order to keep it off of my carpet. However, this isn't a deal-breaker to my overall satisfaction with the desk. Would recommend and would buy again.
Très bon et beau bureau,corespond a mes attentes.
